{"tid":470354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安徽阜陽18死車禍現場V字手勢笑住影相 電台女主播被炒魷","createTime":"2017-11-16T08:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T09:10:37.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c34251b05c446a07e7b8a870999fb60adab7d10","tid":470354,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171116/large/1510809141_9e0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171116%2Flarge%2F1510809141_9e0b.jpg&h=c5ac5bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安徽阜陽昨日發生30車連環相撞車禍，導致18死21傷。安徽當地一名電台女主播，竟然在車禍現場開心自拍，還做出勝利手勢。照片在網上瘋傳，引起內地網民強烈批評。據悉，這名女主播已遭電台解僱。<br />\n<br />\n據內地傳媒報道，這名凌姓女主播隸屬潁上廣播電台，當時她在車禍現場一手拿起自己身上的工作證，一手做出勝利手勢，站在被燒焦的車輛前拍照。另一張照片則是她和一名疑似在現場救援的工作人員合照。<br />\n在死亡現場開心拍照的冷血行為立刻引發網友抨擊。女主播知道犯下大錯後也馬上拍道歉影片貼上網，但為時已晚。潁上廣播電台今日表示，該名凌姓女主播已遭開除，而她的上司亦遭到停職處分。<br />\n另外，昨日事發後，有網民質疑昨日事發時高速公路被霧籠罩，為何當局不封閉高速公路，可是，當地交警稱昨日凌晨起已經實施限速，不能超過每小時60公里，但交警稱事故是事發路段團霧造成的，難以預防，由於並非全路段大霧，因此沒有封閉高速。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171116/57465137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57465137&d=sQ4oYIzeAoHlPV%2Fmw8Dhpf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=cfa4b2a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171116%2F57465137&h=8c61a4c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171116/57465137</a>"},{"pid":"78b0fb41df71bfc4364468819dbec9c0a3173c6c","tid":470354,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:00:40.000Z","msg":"死得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比我直頭開香檳慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc924d343edfe9407d38b2d13adcc269910978f","tid":470354,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77d74b56cb17ac8417a25e60d62fbb634169fa0b","tid":470354,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:10:37.000Z","msg":"不嬲强國救災班友都係咁架啦<br />\n做show之嘛<br />\n被炒原因應該係救援隊未影但佢影左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}